message.content:
Breakfast: Avocado toast with scrambled egg and spinach. 
Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, red onion, and balsamic vinaigrette.
Dinner: Baked salmon with quinoa and steamed vegetables like broccoli and carrots. 
Snack: Greek yogurt with fresh berries and a sprinkle of granola.
Drink plenty of water throughout the day, and don't forget to stay active.
